text: Tetramicra canaliculata is a species of orchids in the subtribe Laeliinae. It is found in Florida, Hispaniola, Puerto Rico, Trinidad and the Lesser Antilles. It is the type species of its genus. == References == == External links == * * * Tetramicra canaliculata at the World Checklist of Selected Plant Families Category:Laeliinae Category:Orchids of the Caribbean Category:Orchids of Florida Category:Plants described in 1918
